---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Refund Policy">
    <main class="relative min-h-screen overflow-hidden">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 pt-32">
            <div class="bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl border border-gray-800/50 p-8 md:p-12">
                <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-8" 
                    style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #c084fc, #818cf8, #38bdf8);
                           -webkit-background-clip: text;
                           -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
                           background-clip: text;">
                    Refund and Cancellation Policy
                </h1>

                <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
                    <div class="text-gray-300 space-y-6">
                        <section>
                            <p class="mb-6 text-lg">
                                This refund and cancellation policy outlines how you can cancel or seek a refund for a product/service that you have purchased through the Platform. Under this policy:
                            </p>
                        </section>

                        <section>
                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Cancellation Policy</h2>
                            
                            <div class="bg-gray-800/50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-700 mb-6">
                                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-purple-300 mb-3">Cancellation Timeline</h3>
                                <p class="mb-4">
                                    Cancellations will only be considered if the request is made <strong class="text-white">within 7 days of placing the order</strong>. However, cancellation requests may not be entertained if:
                                </p>
                                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                                    <li>The orders have been communicated to sellers/merchants listed on the Platform</li>
                                    <li>The service delivery process has been initiated</li>
                                    <li>The product is out for delivery</li>
                                </ul>
                                <p class="mt-4">
                                    In such events, you may choose to reject the product at the doorstep.
                                </p>
                            </div>

                            <div class="bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-600/30 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
                                <p class="text-blue-200">
                                    <strong>Note:</strong> FILLS AI CONSULTANCY does not accept cancellation requests for services that have already been initiated or AI consulting engagements that are in progress.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </section>

                        <section>
                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Refund Policy</h2>
                            
                            <div class="space-y-4">
                                <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-500 pl-4">
                                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Service Quality Issues</h3>
                                    <p class="mb-2">
                                        The refund/replacement can be made if the user establishes that the quality of the service delivered is not as per the agreed specifications or service level agreement.
                                    </p>
                                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
                                        This should be reported <strong>within 7 days of receipt of services</strong>.
                                    </p>
                                </div>

                                <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-500 pl-4">
                                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Reporting Issues</h3>
                                    <p class="mb-2">
                                        In case of receipt of damaged, defective items, or if you feel that the service received is not as described or as per your expectations, please report to our customer service team.
                                    </p>
                                    <p class="mb-2">
                                        The request would be entertained once we have checked and determined the same at our end.
                                    </p>
                                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
                                        This must be brought to our notice <strong>within 7 days of receiving the product/service</strong>.
                                    </p>
                                </div>

                                <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-500 pl-4">
                                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Third-Party Products with Warranty</h3>
                                    <p>
                                        In case of complaints regarding products or services that come with a warranty from third-party providers or manufacturers, please refer the issue directly to them.
                                    </p>
                                </div>

                                <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-500 pl-4">
                                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Refund Processing Time</h3>
                                    <p>
                                        In case of any refunds approved by FILLS AI CONSULTANCY, it will take <strong class="text-white">7 business days</strong> for the refund to be processed to you.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </section>

                        <section>
                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">AI Consulting Services</h2>
                            <div class="bg-gray-800/50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-700">
                                <p class="mb-4">
                                    For AI consulting and development services, the following additional terms apply:
                                </p>
                                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-3">
                                    <li>
                                        <strong>Initial Consultation:</strong> Free consultation calls are non-refundable as they represent time and expertise provided.
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        <strong>Project Deposits:</strong> Project deposits paid at the start of an engagement are non-refundable once work has commenced.
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        <strong>Milestone-Based Projects:</strong> For projects with milestone-based payments, refunds will be calculated based on completed milestones and work delivered.
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        <strong>Subscription Services:</strong> Cancellations for subscription-based services must be made before the next billing cycle to avoid charges.
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </section>

                        <section>
                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">How to Request a Refund</h2>
                            <div class="bg-purple-900/20 border border-purple-600/30 rounded-lg p-6">
                                <p class="mb-4">To request a refund or cancellation:</p>
                                <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-2">
                                    <li>Contact our customer service team through the contact information provided on our website</li>
                                    <li>Provide your order details and reason for refund/cancellation</li>
                                    <li>Include any supporting documentation (screenshots, error messages, etc.)</li>
                                    <li>Our team will review your request within 2-3 business days</li>
                                    <li>You will be notified of the approval or rejection of your refund</li>
                                    <li>If approved, your refund will be processed within 7 business days</li>
                                </ol>
                            </div>
                        </section>

                        <section>
                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Non-Refundable Items/Services</h2>
                            <p class="mb-4">The following are non-refundable:</p>
                            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                                <li>Completed services and delivered projects</li>
                                <li>Custom development work that has been delivered and accepted</li>
                                <li>Training sessions that have been conducted</li>
                                <li>Access fees to proprietary tools and platforms after usage</li>
                                <li>Third-party services purchased on your behalf</li>
                            </ul>
                        </section>

                        <section>
                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Refund Methods</h2>
                            <p class="mb-4">
                                Approved refunds will be processed to the original payment method used during purchase. Depending on your payment provider, it may take additional time for the refund to reflect in your account.
                            </p>
                            <div class="bg-yellow-900/20 border border-yellow-600/30 rounded-lg p-4">
                                <p class="text-yellow-200 text-sm">
                                    <strong>Note:</strong> Processing fees and transaction charges are non-refundable.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </section>

                        <section>
                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
                            <p class="mb-4">
                                For any questions regarding our refund and cancellation policy, or to initiate a refund request, please contact us through the information provided on our website.
                            </p>
                            <div class="bg-gray-800/50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-700">
                                <p class="mb-2"><strong>Company:</strong> FILLS AI CONSULTANCY</p>
                                <p class="mb-2"><strong>Address:</strong> Narsapur, Medak, Telangana, India</p>
                                <p class="mb-2"><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://www.fills.ai/" class="text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300">https://www.fills.ai/</a></p>
                                <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-4">
                                    Customer Service Hours: Monday - Friday (9:00 AM - 6:00 PM IST)
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </section>

                        <div class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-gray-700">
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 text-center">
                                Last Updated: November 2024
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    .prose p {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .prose h2 {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .prose h3 {
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .prose a {
        transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    .prose a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .prose ul, .prose ol {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .prose li {
        line-height: 1.75;
    }
</style>

